{"h9d10a4b7g1cd1g42d3ga59cgbb29ab5c6d99": ["Away! <i>Away!</i>", "e352fae8-f49a-4f1d-b131-ea10af7591c9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "5b55acfa-4c14-e80f-c416-0122802f8f1f"], "h7f948874g7747g41c9gb0bdgd42a8736e2b5": ["Calm down. I won't hurt you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "b6f931e3-7e6a-7dd0-f48c-2c279b95e20a"], "hf881d9d7g0c65g419bga4c8g77fc3d406875": ["You're all the same. Too many of my kind died because of your spears.", "e352fae8-f49a-4f1d-b131-ea10af7591c9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "df16768a-8c3e-0184-1bbc-e20af816692a"], "h20a60269gbde0g40e5g88b0g4432198ea4d6": ["But not me!", "e352fae8-f49a-4f1d-b131-ea10af7591c9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "12e9b87b-43fe-bb90-c0cb-f03b5078361e"], "hadd308d5gadcag4e96g8541g6c6d478316fd": ["Clear off - it's dangerous here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "b4422b11-c738-9d71-0631-9992f1aee610"], "hae53a893gb262g4e8bg904cgf410e831acf1": ["Yes, I have eyes. Keep away from me!", "e352fae8-f49a-4f1d-b131-ea10af7591c9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "cb064559-81fe-03b5-68f1-dc9425ef4e31"], "h3054659ag4a82g4794g9009g9f80046511cb": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "d289bf11-193c-ec8a-3564-c9edead34687"], "h76d3c278g0b90g4974gb69ag110e1dbd068a": ["*Squeeeee!*", "e352fae8-f49a-4f1d-b131-ea10af7591c9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "2b5e848d-d528-6f60-7443-500a492e6181"], "h673154e2g0745g48b7ga790g46618a02fcf2": ["<i>Observe the boar to see what it does.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "5d4c855f-64c2-4539-6c9d-9d36fab09d78"], "hf77ae542g7665g49c4g959dgc0e12fc488ab": ["*Squeeeee!*", "e352fae8-f49a-4f1d-b131-ea10af7591c9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "ae2582e4-53c6-da08-d6ac-93832424a543"], "h357bdb2bgddbbg4864ga60bg3c98fea1211e": ["<i>Raise your palms to calm the boar.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "bb3b1e46-69d0-4373-b57f-d9914b6a616c"], "h73fb4d27g7950g4712g8d9bg2c4715268611": ["*The boar grunts and eyes you warily with its beady eyes.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "9235dc0e-71b0-4126-756b-ab893b32ea94"], "h4d7812d8g50a4g4706gb415g8f383d031c3e": ["Don't worry. I won't harm you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "0a5a641f-65b9-c179-3c50-32ab8867075d"], "hca70ff28g8580g4255gaf0egb0673b5edad7": ["*The boar shuffles its trotters, unsure. Then it dashes away into the wilderness.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "d9d6b15e-7a8d-cc3f-148e-8c4c7a113607"], "h898aa740g9da9g484dg8f0egabc7f45c9c9f": ["<i>Beckon at the boar silently. Try to lure it closer.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "b982fe16-800d-0ad6-eb6b-dd7c903a5d6d"], "hec6808ebg0c33g43fagb4abgea0dbf67df53": ["<i>Attack.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "9c2c094f-3227-5e49-65dc-5a0ec8cf2cdf"], "h982016beg9a64g45ffg9481gf8fc7369755b": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_HarperBooster_ScaredBoar.html", "142ca7f8-7e4e-681d-9f0a-ad14693616bb"]}